    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You might want to look at the changes @palladia made to the start/stop process cmdlets. They relied extensively on P/Invokes, but were reimplemented to use only managed code. IIRC this was guarded to use the new code only on Linux, but we think it may make sense to use it on Windows as well, and remove the old, non-cross-platform code.\n",
